canonical_structure.name: UBX-RXM-MEAS20
canonical_structure.description: Satellite measurements for CloudLocate location service (20 bytes message)

adjudication.reasoning: Both extractions identify the same UBX class (0x02), message ID (0x84), and fixed payload length (20 bytes). The payload structure is consistently described as a single 20-byte array of U1. Extraction 2 includes more metadata keys (like 'unit' and 'reserved'), but the underlying protocol definition is identical to Extraction 1 across both firmware versions (5.10 and 5.30).
